================================================================================
MONGODB NOTICE
================================================================================

This operator manages MongoDB databases but does NOT include, modify, or
redistribute MongoDB software.

MongoDB and the MongoDB logo are trademarks of MongoDB, Inc.

MongoDB Community Server is available under the Server Side Public License (SSPL).
MongoDB Enterprise is available under a commercial license.

Users deploying MongoDB using this operator are responsible for:
1. Obtaining appropriate MongoDB licenses for their use case
2. Complying with MongoDB's trademark usage guidelines
3. Reviewing MongoDB's licensing terms at:
   https://www.mongodb.com/licensing/server-side-public-license

This operator:
- Does NOT distribute MongoDB binaries
- Does NOT modify MongoDB source code
- Only orchestrates deployment of official MongoDB container images
- Is licensed independently under Apache 2.0

================================================================================
CONTAINER IMAGES
================================================================================

This operator references the following container images:

1. mongo (Official MongoDB image)
   - Source: https://hub.docker.com/_/mongo
   - License: MongoDB's licensing terms apply

2. percona/mongodb_exporter (Prometheus Exporter)
   - Source: https://github.com/percona/mongodb_exporter
   - License: Apache 2.0

Users are responsible for reviewing and complying with the licensing terms
of any container images they deploy.
